data.description: Welcome Home !!! 3 bedroom, 1 bath Colonial. Located in the sought after Riverside area of Haverhill is this warm and cozy home offering a timeless blend of comfort, character and suburban charm. Special features include: HARDWOOD FLOORS, Gas fireplace in living room, a nice level lot, off street parking, beautiful covered front porch. This property is a classic home, beautiful grounds on dead end street and in ideal location conveniently located just minutes from groceries, gas, shopping and restaurants, Close to Haverhill’s beautiful Riverside Park and Trinity Stadium   Don’t miss this gem of a home! Flood Insurance is required. Showings deffered until Open house Open house April 13 & 14, 2024 -11am-1 pm
